  <h1>Project Proposal</h1>
  <p>I want to design a user-friendly YA book reccomendations website with the added option of locating an independent book store in their state</p>
  <h2>Project Concept</h2>
  <h3>Objectives and Goals</h3>
  <p>The clients will be able to browse the website for new YA book reccomendations and independent book stores.
  <br>
  The goals of the website is to both introduce consumers to new books and local independent book stores in one platform</p>
  <h3>Intended Audience</h3>
  <p>The intended audience is young adults, particularly those interested in #BookTok.</p>
  <h3>Features</h3>
  <p>Consumers will be able to search for independent book stores by state.
    <br>
    Search for books by release date.
    <br>
    Search for books by author.
    <br>
    Search for books by genre.</p>
